repoman (1.5.0-sg1) lucid; urgency=low

  * Break Debian package into client and server, fix some lintian
    issues.
  * Break base request classes out to common.py, refactor dupe init code
    into get_server() & DEFUALT_URLs.
  * Use python-daemon instead of ncore.become_daemon. Don't use a queue
    for building, fork as needed.
  * Only support JSON serialization through SimpleJSON
  * Ignore build artifacts
  * Update dependencies for the new ncore-less code.
  * Remove unused import.
  * Update dependencies. Setuptools complains if anything listed in
    setup.py's install_requires is missing, so we have to depend on
    everything needed by client and server in both packages.
  * Add missing python-daemon to dependency list.

 -- Ian Eure <ian@simplegeo.com>  Tue, 01 Jun 2010 15:59:16 -0700

